figure.figDesc: Scan of a pencil drawing on blue paper. A lined rectangle takes up a majority of the drawing. A silhouette of something, whether it’s a person or landscape is in the center of the drawing. In both the silhouette and the rectangle has a two lines that cross in it, away from the viewer. To the right of the rectangle is an arrow pointing down at a line. Back of the scan has pencil drawn lines.
